title: Singaravelan
subTitle: Velan's mother tells him to find his cousin, Sumathi, who lives in the city and marry her. Velan sets out to find her with the help of a childhood photograph.

title: Sami Potta Mudichu
subTitle: Kadhirvelan wishes to take revenge on his uncle, who is responsible for his grandfather's death. However, he changes his mind after he meets Neelaveni, his uncle's daughter.

title: Vaidhegi Vanthachu
subTitle: A naive Karupan is forced by his lecherous MLA boss to marry a girl who snubbed the politician. The unwilling bride, turning vengeance into redemption, decides to reform her husband.

title: Simmasanam
subTitle: Sakthivel and Thangarasu are stepbrothers who don't get along with each other. Their differences become more apparent as they start finding out their father's killer.

title: Vasalil Oru Vennila
subTitle: Ammu, a little girl, runs away from her bungalow as her stepmother physically tortures her. However, the girl finds love and solace in the arms of Kamala, a milk vendor.

title: Thedinen Vanthathu
subTitle: A man and his friend try to save a bag containing a hefty sum, which they hide in an empty house. When they return for the bag, the house is occupied by a girl and her family.

title: University
subTitle: A man and a woman connect with each other through a wrong number. Though they talk over the phone regularly and fall in love, they are unaware of the other's identity.
